# Astro Templates

- Astro templates end in a `.astro` extension.
- The typescript code at the top of the templates is separated by three hyphens: `---`
- Don't forget the separators!

## Astro Template Structure

Example: 

```astro
---
// typescript code goes here
---
<div>
  Template markup and HTML goes here.
</div>
```
